vsParam:
Guys, I have something about Netl to tell you.
Do you have time?

Um, of course, Angelica.
What is it?

I want to make peace with Netl.
After all... He's my only little brother.

But I am not good at talking,
so I am thinking about giving him a gift.

Oh, a gift! That's a good idea.
What's in your mind?

Er... the amulet common in my hometown.
My parents... taught me how to make it.

We'd pray for our loved ones to be safe and prosperous
when we make it... so it's a lucky amulet.

Wonderful!
That's the best gift to give when you seek a reconciliation!

Yes. So,
I hope that [px] can help me make the amulet.

Sure, no problem...
What's the style and design of your amulet?

Simply link up the mineral ornament with a specially-made
string will make one beautiful amulet.

I'll make the string...
I want to ask [px] to make the mineral ornament.

I believe that [px] will devote all [px] love to this amulet
just like me...

[px], Angelica.
With this amulet made of your love, he will...

Netl will open his heart!
Ah, but... we also want to help!

Er, yes!
Let Netl also feel our love for him!

Okay, so, let's all work together to help
Netl and Angelica reconcile!
